{"tid":366861,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"紅十字會係咪犯左法","createTime":"2017-08-20T10:31:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T17:56:18.000Z","uid":136683,"like":370,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a38ebdd55b67ff2e353d007c0d218933f1bdd71f","tid":366861,"uid":136683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T10:31:21.000Z","msg":"香港紅十字會創立於1950年，前屬英國紅十字會分會，自1997年7月1日起，隨香港主權移交中國而成為中國紅十字會一個享有高度自治的<span style=\"color: red;\">分會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n基本法第一百四十八條<br />\n香港特別行政區的教育、科學、技術、文化、藝術、體育、專業、醫療衛生、勞工、社會福利、社會工作等方面的民間團體和宗教組織同內地相應的團體和組織的關係，應以<span style=\"color: red;\">互不隸屬</span>、互不干涉和互相尊重的原則為基礎。<br />\n<br />\n《香港紅十字會條例》<br />\n2B.<br />\n與中國紅十字會的<span style=\"color: red;\">隸屬關係</span><br />\n(具追溯力的適應化修訂&mdash;&mdash;見2000年第37號第3條)<br />\n香港紅十字會是中國紅十字會的一個分會，並享有高度自治權；香港紅十字會和中國紅十字會的關係由附表2所列出的中國紅十字會公告所界定。<br />\n<br />\n每年拎咁多政府資助唔知幾多入左強國袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d92d83e02c5ff5e1dfb69f2bd240af8bf780de9","tid":366861,"uid":9543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T12:03:10.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"2eb40e54c5e63406ec2de9c00ce8d0a46a8f514b","tid":366861,"uid":93451,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:55:31.000Z","msg":"留名 等法律jj"},{"pid":"4329f9003d76b46f853fb0e3dfd09d51e7015526","tid":366861,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T14:02:47.000Z","msg":"留名, POST 去紅十字個FACEBOOK <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68c9ac8ffbb7837afce36dd67cbf2c127d400223","tid":366861,"uid":119177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T14:05:12.000Z","msg":"留名睇後續"},{"pid":"878b0acdd58f11825da0ee4d860fea939a393eff","tid":366861,"uid":27664,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T14:07:04.000Z","msg":"你知得太多了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a8d6e27a5012cb15d7aaf8157ec338e3b003eb4","